text:
[Verse]
Under the moonlight
Stars shine bright
We feel so alive
In the night

[Verse 2]
Whispers in the air
Feel the magic there
Hands intertwined
Hearts align

[Chorus]
Jump into the night
Together we'll take flight
Midnight skies so high
We'll never say goodbye

[Verse 3]
Dreams in our mind
Leave the world behind
Just you and me
Set free

[Chorus]
Jump into the night
Together we'll take flight
Midnight skies so high
We'll never say goodbye

[Bridge]
Moonlight as our guide
No need to hide
We'll dance till dawn
Till the shadows are gone
title: Midnight Skies
